gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 100, Suns 95
gameRecap.excerpt: The Lakers defeated the Suns, 100-95. Anthony Davis led the way for the Lakers with 30 points, 12 rebounds, and three blocks, while LeBron James added 21 points, eight rebounds, and nine assists in the victory. Kevin Durant tallied a game-high 39 points (14-28 FG) and 11 rebounds for the Suns in the losing effort. The Lakers improve to 1-1 on the season, while the Suns fall to 1-1.
